    <p>
        Once you've hired a roofing contractor, be prepared to work closely with them when selecting colors and design. They 
        possess the knowledge about materials and construction, but it's your house and you should be an active participant 
        in making decisions.
    </p>
    <p>
        The final step is to let your roofing contractor get to work. Choosing a contractor who is reliable, honest, and 
        hardworking will allow you to enjoy your new roof even more.
    </p>
